Pre-Game Insights: The first seeded sides from Groups B and D (England and South Africa) will be joined by the second seeded sides from Groups A and C (USA and West Indies)
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Super Eights phase of the competition gets underway on June 19, with two matches per day until June 24.
The semi-finals will be played in Tarouba (June 26) and Guyana (June 27), before the final is played in Barbados on June 29.
Others: The Super Eights phase of the competition will be played entirely in the West Indies, with the US leg of the tournament now over.
